defs.docs: Asynchronous channels.

defs.name: mpsc

A multi-producer, single-consumer queue for sending values across
 asynchronous tasks.

defs.name: Sender
defs.docs: A means of transmitting a single value to another task.

defs.docs: Creates a new one-shot channel for sending values across asynchronous tasks.

defs.name: send
defs.docs: Completes this oneshot with a successful result.

defs.docs:

defs.name: is_canceled
defs.docs:
Tests to see whether this `Sender`'s corresponding `Receiver`

defs.name: Canceled
defs.docs:
Error returned from a [`Receiver`](Receiver) when the corresponding
